Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧 未來露西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才一天 怎麼可能填補實力的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.64,0:00:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒有夏·多拉格尼爾那麼厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候到來之前 我們一直待在牢裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.35,0:02:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…露西為什麼會從未來過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了改變最糟糕的未來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最糟糕的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.19,0:02:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…你所在的未來發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在前方等著我們的是絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會有超過一萬頭龍的龍群襲擊這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街道被燒燬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市開始崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,許多人失去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.87,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(640,450)\fad(524,0}轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過一萬頭龍的龍群…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些話…我無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到看到大魔斗比武的結果 我都不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什？ 麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過一萬頭龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會發生這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.93,0:03:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道和那個龍之墓場有關麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出大事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們是從哪裏來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.68,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能沒有任何風聲就潛進來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之不能乾等著 要做戰前準備
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要迎戰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打不過的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都相信我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是騙人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為這種事情不會有人相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要懷疑露西說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未來的我還真是這麼沒出息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要信任自己的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在對自己說教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就說通了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩壞的城堡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌…不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是在哭喊的露西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個龍群來襲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣在城堡中的我們怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏露露 別追問了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都死掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱們會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為和我在一起嗎 所以才會不走運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道過了多少天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我醒過來後 想起來了關於日蝕的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道啟動方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是在忘我地時候打開了大門
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並盲目地相信這樣也許可以回到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我就真的回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了791年7月4日
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不就是最近嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:50.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕只能回到這麼近的過去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 回到400年前打倒澤雷夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:07:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是因為當時日蝕有一部分已經壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向公主進言的神秘未來人就是這個傢伙麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 令人在意的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,街上都是為大魔斗比武攝影的魔水晶屏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想從地下走和傑拉爾他們匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傑拉爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把一切都和他坦白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 他應該在思考對策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在思考對策？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒能從未來帶來解決這件事的對策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道怎樣才能避免那種局勢的發生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從…從未來來的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:07:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人告訴了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕的另一種使用方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2？ 那到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這7年間我們利用大魔斗比武
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為這扇門積累了不少魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.45,0:08:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通過這種方法收集的魔力可以和魔法精靈力相媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…竟然可以和魔法評議院擁有的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說可以毀滅一個國家的神聖之光媲美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將這個力量向龍群發射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是日蝕2計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經向公主建議使用日蝕2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所說的回到了4日前根本就是謊話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要欺騙自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常對不起 這樣一來我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不知道自己是為什麼而來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我一直不知道該怎麼辦才好 只是在街上晃來晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我們一定會想出辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 為了我們的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會扭轉未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一定全是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說未來的露西可能在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼特地…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.92,0:09:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超過一萬條龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日蝕…魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一些前後矛盾的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她故意混亂於未來有關的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.37,0:10:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是露西在說謊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說那個露西本身就是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙敢再說一遍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.26,0:10:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰沒強到誰那種程度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺我漸漸明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:51.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會加入妖精的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也怪你不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那時侯還是個光頭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬著你所在的協會幽鬼支配者的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:15.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我長大以後可以加入幽鬼支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:20.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 它卻在和妖精尾巴的戰爭中敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.98,0:11:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協會也解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此 你還加入了可惡的妖精尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偏偏要加入擊潰幽鬼的協會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.29,0:11:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你加入妖精尾巴一定是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:12:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍咬之虎就沒有這樣的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是會長的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要絕對服從命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利才是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是協會 就應該珍惜同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.99,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,協會是什麼…同伴又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底是為了什麼在戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在終於知道你們為何如此強大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.28,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們贏不了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過過分強大的大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和因為雷克特而覺醒的斯汀可能算是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就什麼都沒明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只青蛙是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青蛙？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛也這麼覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛是隻貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.91,0:13:03.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正確的說是超越者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 弗洛是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.67,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏不了你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看前面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人仍然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然站在你面前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.06,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰 是誰在說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.43,0:13:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格…殺掉伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.05,0:13:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借給你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.51,0:14:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你知道這種路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少想要避免掉大家被王國軍抓住的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下都調查好了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想早點發射信號彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也一定很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:57.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王國軍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會安排在這裏…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心 能用魔法就不會被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿魯卡迪歐斯不見了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.68,0:15:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要擅自這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先不說那個騎士 我們不能放著雪乃不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回去找
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不能分開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧 我們要把這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突破掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米拉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱來保護夏露露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種不安的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:10.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉伽吉魯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是 我的命運…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我借給你力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:34.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是說了什麼比較在意的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就稍微借給你一點力量吧 羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是掌管命運的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不知道什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是要盡情打是吧 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 剛不是還要和解呢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺情況有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯 要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵龍劍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龍的連雀閃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅格？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影龍的斬擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初代 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是被什麼附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊 剛剛變成影子也還能抓到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力的質變了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常 非常邪惡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的知識中不存在的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然沒有夏·多拉格尼爾那樣厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:16.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個夏·多拉格尼爾也打不過現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個魔力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:32.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在城鎮方向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜 未來露西被捲進戰鬥中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有夏他們在就不必慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 露西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些傢伙明明是小鬼 怎麼這麼強
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喚對魔法部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓他們從這裏過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.28,0:19:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備第二波第三波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,國家也有魔法部隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇我一跳 就用這種魔法和專業的打？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒效果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這小鬼是怪物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 久等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒在等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擅自出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？ 費歐雷王國最強的魔法兵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太盛大啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法師嗎？ 不是星靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒那樣的星靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要調教呢 公主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了美麗的翡翠公主 讓我好好活躍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把同伴也捲進來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各種意義上都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力氣還挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體力我還挺有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是能伸長？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 自稱是最強我們就盡全力上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:24.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 看我把你的全力擋下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍的鐵拳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.14,0:00:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是那個伽吉魯嗎 丟死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 他會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伽吉魯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗洛必須要去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得讓他把羅格還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子會侵蝕你 然後你會永遠消失
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在黑暗中沉眠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火龍神能做到 我沒道理做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.72,0:21:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.47,0:21:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把影子…吃掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起 真做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸收了影的屬性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:38.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你快滾出那傢伙的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從羅格？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 他的名字不叫羅格
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的小弟萊歐斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是憧憬我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:22:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候我不是那樣的人 我自己最清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.18,0:22:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就再讓你回想起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.97,0:22:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的恐怖之處
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:19.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵影龍？！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:24:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 伽吉魯那傢伙把影子吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有資格說別人麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.62,0:24:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏還不是能吃火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影子和火不一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火是食物 而且很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.21,0:24:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你來說確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還這不理解有人居然能吃影子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱對你們這種類型的都看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 激雷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我就推薦點好吃的火給哈比吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.77,0:24:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏 這就算了

